Name: Testcase 1
Query: plot mean mpg and model_year for all cylinders
Output:
df_tt = df.groupby(['cylinders','model_year']).mean().groupby(['cylinders'])
for cc, df_tt1 in df_tt:
    df_tt2 = df_tt1.reset_index()
    plt.scatter(x=df_tt2["model_year"], y=df_tt2["mpg"], label=str(cc))
plt.xlabel('model_year')
plt.ylabel('mean mpg')
plt.legend(title='cylinders')
